column5: Late Sept Walleye fishing has been not to bad for the this fall ...fish have moved much shallower this fall in the 58 to 65 fow range ...Big dipsy on a 2 setting back 145 useing anything Green in a worm Harness ...also 10 color lead core has been my Hottest rods ...get out and enjoy before the lake gets to cold ...
